text: Susanne Standish-White (born 3 November 1956) is a Zimbabwean rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Zimbabwe Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Harare
